      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>chorizo has crisped, reduce the heat to medium and add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add the <strong>drained gluten free linguine</strong> with a few splashes of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
