    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>clotted cream </strong>and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Tip: Add more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p><p>Add a squeeze of <strong>lemon </strong>and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>chorizo & lemon gluten free linguine</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
