      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chorizo & lemon gluten free linguine </strong>topped with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>zingy salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
